Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.48,0:00:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新機動戰記-鋼彈W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.68,0:00:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.15,0:00:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.69,0:00:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.80,0:00:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著你被淋濕的肩膀 想溫暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.01,0:00:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,顫抖的指尖 徬徨地在找甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.81,0:00:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的視線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.09,0:01:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲傷變為力量的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.53,0:01:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.20,0:01:13.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決不褪色的熾熱思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.84,0:01:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.54,0:01:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙不需的是要我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.10,0:01:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可以戰鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.34,0:01:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二十七話\N[勝利和敗北的軌跡]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，希洛仍然下落不明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.16,0:02:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要笑，爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.03,0:02:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N我現在也聽到希洛的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，我相信他一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個山克王國出現啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.77,0:02:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之後，過了多久呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自從遇上他之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.89,0:02:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時，我和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.76,0:02:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一起在前往地球的穿梭機裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.66,0:02:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸，那是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.20,0:02:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.47,0:02:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我遇上包含了衛星\N的願望的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.77,0:02:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有一部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一切從這裡開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.16,0:03:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動代號，希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派給我的任務只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.74,0:04:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是個小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.02,0:04:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳看到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.05,0:04:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.65,0:04:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.22,0:04:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.37,0:04:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是…\N我是莉莉娜‧德利安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.68,0:04:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之前的我只是一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.45,0:04:47.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒付出任何代價就享受幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知天高地厚的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.12,0:04:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，遇上他後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.46,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的命運大大改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那男孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.97,0:05:04.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是希洛‧唯，多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.77,0:05:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有錯，是他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.75,0:05:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天是我的生日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.82,0:05:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要光臨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太…太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.70,0:05:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要殺死妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在流星作戰裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,降落地球的鋼彈駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.58,0:05:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只我一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重武裝鋼彈的駕駛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特洛瓦‧巴頓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.22,0:05:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙漠鋼彈的駕駛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.73,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卡特爾‧拿巴伯‧溫拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.89,0:06:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.33,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.04,0:06:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不可以戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.62,0:06:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請別這樣，因為是我先走出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停車!不停車我就攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小孩?少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.65,0:07:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這少年單人匹馬攻擊基地?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以很天真
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.60,0:07:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神龍鋼彈的駕駛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.64,0:07:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,張五飛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是甚麼光?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.19,0:07:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人!敵人呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有，死神鋼彈的駕駛者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迪歐‧麥斯威爾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:51.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，你在做甚麼?告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是甚麼人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.77,0:07:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是魚雷吧，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想知道你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說話，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.15,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.95,0:08:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳太多事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.67,0:08:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這情形怎樣看\N你也比較像壞人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.60,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒受傷吧?小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.34,0:08:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒事吧?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.65,0:08:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別勉強啊，因為你是傷者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.09,0:08:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.19,0:08:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和這個人有何仇怨?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.76,0:08:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，雖然好像有點內情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.06,0:08:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但立即離開這裡比較好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為了妳的安全著想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.67,0:08:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還要來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.90,0:09:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒當其他鋼彈駕駛員是同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.81,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，一開始我就沒有同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個自稱迪歐的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也和莉莉娜一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.58,0:09:13.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是執行任務的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.85,0:09:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣，一切完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.32,0:09:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務完成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.87,0:09:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當時，爸爸你強烈希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.57,0:09:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球和衛星和平共存呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.81,0:09:41.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的報告我聽過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望德利安外務次官你退席
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.38,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經明言也無所謂了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.85,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真正危險的人是你們自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.36,0:09:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後\N爸爸帶著我再次前往宇宙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.36,0:09:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是爸爸你最後的關懷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.00,0:10:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓我看美麗的地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.31,0:10:09.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們想怎樣處置我爸爸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.95,0:10:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.98,0:10:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.62,0:10:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…不是…妳真正的爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.86,0:10:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳的真名是…\N莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.00,0:10:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳是以前提倡和平主義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.33,0:10:36.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,匹斯克拉福特王族的公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.20,0:10:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心OZ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.34,0:10:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…爸爸!你不要死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有關希洛‧唯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在聖米加勒學園的資料，取消
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,轉校手續，OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.43,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又要去戰鬥嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.07,0:11:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一個任務在哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.71,0:11:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了你的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.81,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，比起我自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.51,0:11:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛是衛星派來的\N鋼彈駕駛員一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.71,0:11:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許對於我的生活方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.55,0:11:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有更大的影響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛，我知道太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.33,0:11:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,始終要死呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.67,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前不想一無所知就死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但現在不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.51,0:11:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我明白你戰鬥的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.88,0:11:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在也和希洛你在戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.51,0:11:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我戰鬥?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在做甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.84,0:12:28.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人應該死掉較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.35,0:13:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.08,0:13:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃避，我求你，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球圈統一聯合最高司令官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.07,0:13:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾邊塔元帥\N希望和衛星和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.41,0:13:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,計劃想大幅裁軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，OZ的統帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.48,0:13:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.98,0:13:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以巧妙的情報手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.45,0:13:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令希洛他們齊集新愛德華基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.42,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後，借鋼彈的手消滅聯合軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.51,0:14:06.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別衝動啊，年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.15,0:14:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二幕開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.49,0:14:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我會很忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.16,0:14:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作戰名稱[黎明行動]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.79,0:14:25.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場準備周詳的政變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由佈署在各地聯合軍基地的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ士兵和SMS進行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們一日之內就令聯合崩潰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.44,0:14:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就讓你嘗嘗革命的滋味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.21,0:14:42.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯合的時代已經結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新的統一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.68,0:14:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要由我們OZ親手創立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.39,0:14:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和新秩序一起建立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著，OZ的上級特校蕾蒂‧安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.10,0:15:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提出了把宇宙用機動戰士陶拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運去西伯利亞基地的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那是一併殲滅鋼彈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.74,0:15:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聲東擊西戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其他鋼彈會來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.41,0:15:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有我們應付不來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.51,0:15:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，另外4個鋼彈一定會來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:42.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.74,0:15:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,互相認定是最強敵人而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.38,0:15:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不得不接受這挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.85,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,身為鋼彈的駕駛員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.92,0:16:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到有這麼大威力的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聯絡宇宙要塞巴爾吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各部鋼彈的駕駛員聽住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.63,0:16:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們準備好用飛彈\N攻擊殖民衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.14,0:16:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員現在馬上投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把鋼彈交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.64,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星被瞄準了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫我交出鋼彈?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.71,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ的要脅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.95,0:16:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還能戰鬥吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.63,0:16:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ聽好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.36,0:16:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不到你們是這麼愚蠢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.20,0:16:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了勝利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.80,0:16:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊衛星這等違反人道的行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.70,0:16:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是不得已吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.71,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這裡宣佈投降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.18,0:16:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但鋼彈不能交出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.55,0:16:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重覆，我投降\N但鋼彈不能交出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.32,0:17:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,任務，明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.02,0:17:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥啊，希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.29,0:17:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也前往自己的戰場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,羅姆斐拉財團想以名為支配的形式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.36,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,維持和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果繼續戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.67,0:17:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那或許有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.54,0:17:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\N在許多人犧牲後君臨天下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.67,0:17:56.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我絕對不會容許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為山克王國的後裔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.08,0:18:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜‧匹斯克拉福特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.11,0:18:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.85,0:18:05.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,衛星被當作擋箭牌就束手無策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.95,0:18:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，傑克斯修理好我的鋼彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.62,0:18:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望繼續西伯利亞那場決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥的地點是南極
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.93,0:18:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有接受傑克斯的好意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.50,0:18:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用特洛瓦的重武裝鋼彈決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.63,0:18:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，這場決鬥有何意義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.77,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找尋要保護的東西的男人和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.44,0:18:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,失去保護辦法的男人的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.39,0:18:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰也會為過去\N所犯的錯誤而痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.80,0:18:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我們還年輕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們應該想著創造未來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.67,0:19:04.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想結束這場無意義的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.36,0:19:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是要那樣才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.97,0:20:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.27,0:20:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在馬上停止這場決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.38,0:20:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳就用那雙眼看著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥有多污穢!有多卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真過份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.49,0:20:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是戰士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是匹斯克拉福特的騎士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他沒理由能做出那麼卑鄙的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.02,0:20:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉莉娜小姐，諾茵特尉來電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.86,0:20:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,諾茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.76,0:20:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我誤會了妳是個更真誠的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.43,0:20:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.97,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被妳鄙視也沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.41,0:20:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信傑克斯特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.48,0:20:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會出言反對他想做的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.31,0:20:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!打倒傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.88,0:20:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!莉莉娜殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.25,0:20:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是甚麼命運的安排也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.79,0:20:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望自己哥哥身亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不經思考的想法，請妳停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.83,0:21:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甚麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的王兄?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.26,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.30,0:21:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我第一次知道傑克斯是我王兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多運輸機從3時方向接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.34,0:21:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽到嗎?希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有你，傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.68,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是30部運輸機\N包括艾亞利玆也只有100部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.28,0:21:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去引開他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.12,0:21:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光榮歸於衛星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.22,0:21:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傑克斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後和我交手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.36,0:21:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是傑克斯‧馬吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是米利亞爾特‧匹斯克拉福特?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰都好\N如果成為任務的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.63,0:21:41.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只好打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.20,0:21:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果始終是敵人，我就殺死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.64,0:21:50.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那次之後\N我就沒見過哥哥和希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.11,0:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,世界踏上更混亂之途
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.44,0:21:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在，OZ一分為二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.45,0:21:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繼續著愚蠢的戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.72,0:22:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了結束這場戰爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.75,0:22:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定會在我的面前出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.32,0:22:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希洛!快點回來我身邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待續
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.48,0:22:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心血來潮的找人出來\N只因為天氣好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.48,0:22:38.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我一直等不到人\N你以為你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.48,0:22:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你是跑過來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那也是應該的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.98,0:22:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love ! 那個惹人厭的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.48,0:23:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉弄人  是因為心理有愛意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.98,0:23:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Just Love !  老是讓人掛念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.48,0:23:17.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起\N我不該說出強人所難的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.48,0:23:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,‧‧‧Just Love‧‧‧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.77,0:23:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,次回予告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.54,0:23:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要這個世上有人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.45,0:23:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰鬥就絕對不會消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.98,0:23:40.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而否定戰鬥不是和平之路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.55,0:23:46.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯‧克修里那達\N從歷史的表面舞台消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.22,0:23:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.23,0:23:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯在不斷交錯的命運裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.06,0:23:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又即將顯示新的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.53,0:23:55.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新機動戰記-鋼彈W，第二十八話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.70,0:23:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,交錯的命運

